Vendored Tesseract trained data files (vendor/tessdata/*.traineddata) are
distributed under Apache-2.0 by their upstream maintainers (tesseract-ocr
project). See https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tessdata_fast for details.

Native scanner binaries that may be installed at runtime via apt
(djvulibre-bin, p7zip-full, tesseract-ocr) retain their distribution
licenses (GPL-2.0+ family). They are invoked as subprocesses and not
linked, so their licenses do not extend to Bibliary's source.
